TEXT(beginproblem());
$showPartialCorrectAnswers = 1;

$a = random(2,20,1);
$b = random(2,20,1);

TEXT(EV2(<<EOT));

Suppose that \( f(x) = (x+$a)^{$b} e^{x} \).  Find \(f'(0)\).

$BR $BR

\(f'(0)\) = \{ans_rule(30) \}
$BR

EOT

$ans = $a**$b + $b*($a)**($b-1);
ANS(num_cmp($ans));

